headline: Keysight Recognized on TIME’s List of the World’s Most Sustainable Companies of 2025
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., August 06, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS), has been recognized as one of the World’s Most Sustainable Companies of 2025, listed in the second edition rankings from TIME and Statista. This is Keysight’s second consecutive year of inclusion on the ranking of the top 500 most sustainable companies, and the company is proud to announce that it has significantly improved its position in this year’s rankings, rising from 247th in 2024 to 127th in 2025.
